  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 1st level, you can use dexterity for Kōsoku attack rolls and Save DC calculations. Your unarmed damage die becomes a d4 when using Kōsoku hijutsu and taijutsu with the Wind Release keyword. If your unarmed damage is higher than a d4, it increases by 1 step, up to a d12. Your fantastic speed is not without style.</p><p>At 3rd level, you may run on walls, ceilings, or water at no movement penalty without needing to spend any chakra. If you end your turn on a wall or ceiling then you fall 10 feet at the end of every subsequent turn. If you end your turn on water then you immediately sink.</p>",
